@startuml
' @id(SEQ-ELEMENT-DESC)
' @ref(USE-ELEMENT-DESC)
'
' Current-side flow as implemented: descriptions are extracted once at
' startup (Project::descriptions via extract_descs) and the selected
' @id's text is rendered in a distinct DESCRIPTION frame.
'
' @desc(SEQ-ELEMENT-DESC, "As-built: MddViewer::new caches Project::descriptions(); the MODEL CONTEXT card renders descriptions.get(selected_id) in a colored Frame, else a weak placeholder.")
title Show a diagram element's description (current)

actor "Developer" as Dev
participant "MddViewer::new" as New
participant "Project::descriptions\n(extract_descs)" as Core
participant "MddViewer::update\n(context panel)" as Card

New -> Core : descriptions()
Core -> Core : regex @desc(<ID>, "text")\nover model + constraint files
Core --> New : BTreeMap<String,String>
New -> New : store self.descriptions

Dev -> Card : select an @id (IDS list)
Card -> Card : self.selected_id = Some(id)
alt descriptions has id
  Card -> Card : Frame (accent stroke + id in yellow)\nitalic description text
else missing
  Card -> Card : weak "No description for this element"
end
Card --> Dev : DESCRIPTION block in MODEL CONTEXT
@enduml
